#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "The GNU Manifesto (which appears below) was written by <a href=\"http://"
#| "www.stallman.org/\">Richard Stallman</a> at the beginning of the GNU "
#| "Project, to ask for participation and support.  For the first few years, "
